<idea-plugin>
    <id>aid.dev.jscp</id>
    <name>Jscp</name>
    <version>0.8.3</version>
    <vendor email="04637@163.com" url="https://www.aid.dev">阳光彩虹小白马Plus</vendor>

    <description><![CDATA[
    <h2>一键部署插件, 将文件上传至服务器并执行指定命令, 将服务器日志输出在 IntelliJ IDEs 控制台</h2>
        <hr>
        <h3>设置: File => Settings => Tools => Jscp Plugin</h3>
        <br>
        <p>配置说明: </p>
        <ul>
            <li>Server ip: 服务器IP, 会将文件上传至该ip</li>
            <li>Ssh port: 服务器ssh端口, 默认22</li>
            <li>Server ip: 服务器IP, 会将文件上传至该ip</li>
            <li>Ssh port: 服务器ssh端口, 默认22</li>
            <li>User name: 服务器登录用户名</li>
            <li>Password: 登录密码</li>
            <li>Remote dir: 文件将上传至服务器上的该目录</li>
            <li>Local dir/file: 选择本地待上传的目录/文件</li>
            <li>Deploy cmd: 文件上传完成后将执行该命令 (示例: 重启tomcat并获取日志输出) <code>source /etc/profile&&${TOMCAT_HOME}/bin/shutdown.sh&&${TOMCAT_HOME}/bin/startup.sh&&tail -f ${TOMCAT_HOME}/logs/catalina.out</code></li>
        </ul>
        <p>使用: </p>
        <ul>
            <li>IDEs右上角Build左侧蓝色按钮, 点击执行</li>
        </ul>
        <hr>
        <a href="https://github.com/04637/go-pscp">https://github.com/04637/go-pscp</a><br>
        <a href="https://github.com/04637/jscp-plugin">https://github.com/04637/jscp-plugin</a><br>
    ]]>
    </description>

    <change-notes><![CDATA[
    <ul>
      <li><emb>更新插件描述</emb></li>
      <li><emb>添加详细设置项说明</emb></li>
      <li><emb>提升用户体验</emb></li>
    </ul>
    <hr/>
    <a href="https://github.com/04637/jscp-plugin/blob/master/README.md">https://github.com/04637/jscp-plugin/blob/master/README.md</a>
    ]]>
    </change-notes>

    <!-- please see http://www.jetbrains.org/intellij/sdk/docs/basics/getting_started/build_number_ranges.html for description -->
    <idea-version since-build="183.0" />

    <!-- please see http://www.jetbrains.org/intellij/sdk/docs/basics/getting_started/plugin_compatibility.html
         on how to target different products -->
    <depends>com.intellij.modules.platform</depends>

    <extensions defaultExtensionNs="com.intellij">
        <!-- Add your extensions here -->
    </extensions>

    <actions>
        <action id="dev.aid.jscp.DeployAction" class="dev.aid.jscp.DeployAction"
            text="Deploy project" description="Deploy project" icon="/icons/up2.svg">
            <add-to-group group-id="NavBarToolBar" anchor="before"
                relative-to-action="ToolbarRunGroup" />
        </action>
    </actions>
    <extensions defaultExtensionNs="com.intellij">
        <projectService serviceImplementation="dev.aid.jscp.settings.JscpState" />
        <projectConfigurable parentId="tools" instance="dev.aid.jscp.settings.JscpConfigurable"
            id="dev.aid.jscp.settings.JscpConfigurable" displayName="Jscp Plugin"
            nonDefaultProject="true" />
        <!--<toolWindow id="Jscp" icon="/icons/up2.svg" anchor="bottom"-->
        <!--    factoryClass="com.intellij.execution.dashboard.RunDashboardToolWindowFactory" />-->
        <toolWindow id="Jscp" icon="/icons/up2.svg"
            anchor="bottom" factoryClass="dev.aid.jscp.window.MyToolWindowFactory"/>
    </extensions>
</idea-plugin>